76
00:06:11,511 --> 00:06:17,551
Suster bilang padaku kau pernah ke sini, jadi kau mungkin tahu.

77
00:06:17,671 --> 00:06:18,671
Apa?

78
00:06:19,211 --> 00:06:21,851
Pria bernama Rikumichi Kusuda.

79
